data.description: Wouldn't it be nice to move into a house knowing that a lot of the big ticket items have been updated? Here's your chance! This split floor plan, 3 bed, 2 bath home has a new roof, new HVAC, and new hot water heater. It is sitting on 5 acres, with lots of opportunities for homesteading or hunting! Some of the other things you'll love about this home include the circle drive, updated primary bathroom, bonus room, abundance of square footage AND the covered gazebo that could be your own personal oasis! Call your favorite Realtor to set up a showing, and to start making plans for your dream home!
